<section>
<h2>Privacy Policy</h2>
<p><b>Effective Date:</b> 24/04/2026</p>

<p>This bot does not collect or store personal data outside Discord.</p>

<p>It may temporarily use user ID, server ID, channel ID, and message content only to execute commands.</p>

<p>No data is sold, shared, or used for advertising.</p>

<p>Removing the bot from your server removes any temporary usage data.</p>
</section>

<section>
<h2>Terms of Service</h2>

<p>By using this bot, you agree to these terms.</p>

<p>The bot is provided "as is" and may change or stop anytime.</p>

<p>Do not spam, abuse, or exploit the bot.</p>

<p>We are not responsible for any damage caused by using the bot.</p>
</section>

